Concept ACK

It works for me:

```powershell
# unzip https://github.com/sipsorcery/qt_win_binary/releases/download/qt51210x64_vs2019_1694/Qt5.12.10_x64_static_vs2019_1694.zip to C:\Qt5.12.10_x64_static_vs2019_1694
cd build_msvc
python msvc-autogen.py  # as a substution for "py -3 msvc-autogen.py"
msbuild /m bitcoin.sln /p:Platform=x64 /p:Configuration=Release /t:build
```
